Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:14.09,0:03:15.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,干嘛啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:15.82,0:03:16.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我也要去!
