Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:46.15,0:03:48.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哎呀莉采儿，回来的真快呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:48.46,0:03:50.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因为老公又把我丢回来了!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:50.66,0:03:52.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哎呀，那真是太好了呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:52.99,0:03:54.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在做什么呢?
