Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:16.72,0:08:18.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,照片...?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:19.36,0:08:20.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你看了这个吗!?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:20.86,0:08:22.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你看了一定会大吃一惊的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:23.23,0:08:24.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就跟老公喜欢的一模一样呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:24.87,0:08:27.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我...我才没有说喜欢这种的啦...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:27.17,0:08:28.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要去罗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:30.61,0:08:34.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,锵锵~快看啊老公~
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:34.81,0:08:36.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎么样啊?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:36.81,0:08:39.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那那那什么打扮啊!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:39.31,0:08:43.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就说啦是老公最喜欢的啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:48.96,0:08:52.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊，老公，要出门吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:53.96,0:08:57.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哇~第一次跟老公一起出门呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:57.83,0:08:59.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,把这包裹给我寄到北部的边境去!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:59.97,0:09:01.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,包裹...是指这个吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:02.20,0:09:04.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,当然啊!这不管怎么看都是包裹吧!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:04.97,0:09:07.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哇，是包裹，是包裹耶\N(还在说话呢...)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:07.48,0:09:10.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,会说话的包裹啦!帮我寄航空限时
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:10.58,0:09:11.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:11.35,0:09:14.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你们广告上说什么都能送\N难道是骗人的!?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:14.08,0:09:16.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不过是个会说话的包裹\N就没法送了吗!?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:16.72,0:09:18.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,当...当然行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:18.22,0:09:20.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,让你瞧瞧专业的本领!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:20.86,0:09:22.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,(到北部边境)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:24.73,0:09:26.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,拜托你们啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:37.37,0:09:38.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,(到北部边境)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:40.24,0:09:43.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,咦?能从这里出去吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:43.61,0:09:45.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,行了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:46.15,0:09:52.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我在往下掉耶~!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:59.29,0:10:01.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,老公我回来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:01.90,0:10:05.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你、你怎么会!?\N为、为什么!?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:05.63,0:10:12.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我也不太清楚\N不过很刺激很好玩喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:13.27,0:10:17.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这一点也不好玩~!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:17.65,0:10:20.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我还有另一件老公你喜欢的喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:20.65,0:10:21.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什么!?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:27.29,0:10:27.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,开玩笑的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:28.06,0:10:32.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,为什么我非喜欢水手服运动短裤\N龟甲缚还有裸体围裙不可啊!?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:35.93,0:10:39.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是这边的书里面夹着的照片\N穿的就是这样啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:40.07,0:10:41.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这里的书...?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:46.31,0:10:48.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这、这是什么照片啊!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:49.08,0:10:50.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎样，我扮的很像吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:51.31,0:10:53.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊，老公!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:54.08,0:10:57.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是谁把这种东西藏在我书架上的啊!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:57.32,0:11:01.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,等一下嘛，老公~
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:04.19,0:11:05.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是老爸吗!?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:05.46,0:11:08.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这是从那种杂志上扫瞄下来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:08.20,0:11:10.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,再把它像照片一样印出来的吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:10.83,0:11:12.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要是被老婆看到就不妙了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:12.47,0:11:14.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以就藏到友纪的房间
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:14.37,0:11:16.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,您是有那种癖好吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:16.87,0:11:19.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,呃，这个嘛...是的...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:19.47,0:11:21.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,自己收起来嘛，真是...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:23.61,0:11:25.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真是个大傻瓜呢...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:25.48,0:11:27.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是我一时糊涂，我马上把它扔了!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:28.12,0:11:29.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,莉采儿啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:29.35,0:11:30.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:30.35,0:11:33.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,男人啊就是一种那么傻的生物
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:33.72,0:11:34.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:34.49,0:11:37.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不过好歹这个人还是有他的优点的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:38.23,0:11:39.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,没有啦...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:39.63,0:11:42.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,重要的是\N看你要被一无是处的男人骗去呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:42.63,0:11:45.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,还是要选一个不是那样的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:45.13,0:11:46.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:46.37,0:11:50.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,友纪嘛...是属于哪一种呢...?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:51.01,0:11:53.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哼!那种事谁知道啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:53.01,0:11:56.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不过在这个时代还真是俯拾即是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:56.88,0:11:58.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真不像话，像我们那个时候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:58.88,0:12:00.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是要拼老命才弄得到呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:00.75,0:12:02.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如今什么都看的一清二楚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:02.38,0:12:05.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,反而让人失去了那种小小的幸福感
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:05.39,0:12:07.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,确实是...脱光光虽然也不错
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:07.15,0:12:09.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不过半裸才是好色之人的正道啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:09.89,0:12:12.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这种无聊的事不要聊那么爽!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:12.66,0:12:15.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,随他们去吧，来吃晚饭喽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:15.40,0:12:16.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哇，好好吃的样子喔!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:16.93,0:12:18.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你想穿这样到什么时候啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:18.53,0:12:19.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,咦，不行吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:20.03,0:12:27.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就算你穿成这样也没办法让人\N有一丁点儿的感觉啦! 白痴~!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:27.27,0:12:31.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哇，是我不好是我不好!别哭啊!
