Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:56.30,0:12:59.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,冲啊! 冲啊! 冲啊!\N老公啊!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:59.94,0:13:03.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,最喜欢你了 冲啊冲啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:10.18,0:13:13.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,男人和女人真是难以理解
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:13.59,0:13:17.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,为了查清楚我去了图书馆
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:17.49,0:13:20.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,虽然对比他年幼的我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:20.46,0:13:25.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,老公是一点兴趣也没有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:25.50,0:13:32.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是人家好喜欢你，所以我不会哭的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:32.47,0:13:39.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不气馁，不逃避，更不会失去勇气
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:39.48,0:13:42.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,相信总有一天春天会到来的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:42.85,0:13:52.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,拿出认真的力量，认真的力量往前冲
